Changelog

Source: NEWS.md

modeldata (development version) Unreleased

modeldata 0.1.0 2020-10-22

  • Add the grant acceptance data from Kuhn and Johnson (2013) (Applied Predictive Modeling).

  • The crickets data from Chapter 3 of tmwr.org were added.

modeldata 0.0.2 2020-06-22

  • The bivariate dataset was missing, this has been corrected (@mdogucu, #5).

  • The Ames and penguin data sets were added.

modeldata 0.0.1 2019-12-06

  • Added a NEWS.md file to track changes to the package.

Contents

modeldata is a part of the tidymodels ecosystem, a collection of modeling packages designed with common APIs and a shared philosophy.

Developed by Max Kuhn. Site built by pkgdown.
